{
  "stem": "8703.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they sent us what they called aussenkommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Aussenkommando, they send us to a place which is called Schlieben.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Schlieben.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Over there was also HASAG, the same place as in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The same company owned it, and we-- and they were producing also armaments for the army over there in that place, in that Schlieben.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "HASAG.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They called it HASAG, Hugo Schneider and Company, they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These HASAG people, they own-- they took over almost all the weapon factories from Poland that they were in existence.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't pay a penny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They paid for each prisoner-- each slave prisoner-- they paid about four zloty to the SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't care-- they-- they didn't mind if we are not getting any food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were really responsible I heard that, after the war, they didn't even sue the family who own the HASAG.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what I heard, I read later on that the owner, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Boudin ?], I think was his name, and his wife committed suicide or it was just an explosion in one of their factories and they were killed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, we came over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The atmosphere was entirely different in [INAUDIBLE] that we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans saw what was going on, that the end is nearing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were over there from a whole-- a whole winter over there, from August-- end of August to April 15th, working in ammunition factories.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was much, much-- number one, the soup, the food that we got was better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't the watery soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was much better over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bil-- the man who was responsible for our place was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
